author: Khaleda Rahman
title: Grant Hackett's breakup with girlfriend led to breakdown | Daily Mail Online
text: How Grant Hackett's 'breakup with glamorous girlfriend sparked his breakdown' - as it's revealed he had to be 'RESTRAINED by security after incident at Michael Phelps' wedding' Grant Hackett has been located by police in Queensland on Thursday evening Olympic star had been missing since 7.30am on Thursday, his father said He was reportedly last seen at the Palazzo Versace hotel on the Gold Coast His family pleaded with the public to help find the 36-year-old Olympian Hours before, he posted a photo to social media showing him with a black eye Hackett claimed his brother had beaten him and described him as 'angry' Olympic swimmer was arrested on Wednesday afternoon at his parents' home He was released hours later without charge and is seeking rehab treatment Published: 15:03 GMT, 16 February 2017 | Updated: 09:15 GMT, 17 February 2017 115 shares
